OL,11,CSunday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,12,Fwith some sunny spells, some cloud
OL,13,Fbubbling up by afternoon. Warm.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA dry
OL,16,Fand very warm few days with some
OL,17,Fsunshine. More in the way of cloud
OL,18,Fpossible by Wednesday.
